{"type": "article", "id": 26909, "title": "像星球一样的灯具", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-17T06:45:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702114959JGxOMoCI8493KYLb.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>这组漂亮的灯具是纽约设计师 <a href=\"http://www.harryallendesign.com/home.htm\">Harry Allen</a> 和波特兰玻璃工作室 <a href=\"http://esque-studio.com/\">Esque Studio</a> 第二次合作的产物。每一件均由手工吹制的玻璃和水刀切割的金属片组合而成，制作过程中的差异最终也反应在了独一无二的成品上，看起来很像是宇宙中造型各异的星球。Harry Allen Esque 灯具系列目前正在纽约的 <a href=\"http://www.hellergallery.com/\">Heller Gallery</a> 进行展出，展览将持续到 5 月 28 日。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021149578PnsdvA9V1gotGIa.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76528117\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114957teKYT4xldwBPo0qD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64547677\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114958Lx2tWISk9jrXAJcF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.04645477\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114958gfdGM2Na9qmTe0k8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}